                    <h3>Cancellation &amp; Rescheduling</h3>
                    <p>Cancellations do not qualify for refunds. One time rescheduling is allowed free of charge if requested at least <span class="highlight-text">24-48 hours</span> before session. Retainers are valid for 12 months.</p>
