                    <h3>Selection &amp; Turnaround</h3>
                    <p>Clients select their final images from an unedited JPEG gallery hosted online. Final processed files are delivered within 2 to 4 working days via a secure online gallery <span class="highlight-text">valid for 1 month</span>. The original, unedited camera RAW files can be downloaded if requested and paid for.</p>
