                <div class="protocol-item">
                    <h3>Image Rights &amp; Usage</h3>
                    <p>Clients are granted a <span class="highlight-text">non-exclusive personal-use license</span> for sharing and printing. Libertypictures retains <span class="highlight-text">full ownership</span> of all images, and may share selected images for <span class="highlight-text">portfolio or promotional purposes</span>.</p>
